    <h2>About Paul Schiek</h2>
 

  <p>Paul Schiek will someday build his own house. For now, he proudly calls the city of Oakland his home. In 2003 he founded "These Birds Walk", the moniker under which he has published three of his own photo books. His commercial work has appeared in magazines such as Big, Slap, and Vice, and on numerous record albums. Paul attended the California College of Arts and Crafts, where he received his BFA in photography. He was born in Fond du Lac, Wisconsin, 27 years ago.</p>

